2. Confirm Booking (status: &apos;confirmed&apos;)
3. Set slot_state to &apos;booked&apos;
4. Create Scheduled Session &amp;amp; Jitsi Room
5. Dispatch FCM Push Notifications" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#4e4e4e;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
